examples.en: A few random shots were fired.

She took three shots and missed every time.
It took him four shots to get to the green.

When it comes to getting shots, I'm a real baby.
I managed to get some good shots of the carnival.

It was a job in which she was able to call the shots.
As shots rang out, the crowd ran screaming in all directions.
If a goalie saves 96 out of 100 shots, his save percentage is 96 percent.
Troops fired tear gas and shots to disperse a crowd of 15,000 demonstrators.
At least 30 shots were fired in a matter of seconds (=in a very short time).
Two shots rang out (=could be heard), and security guards rushed over, guns drawn.
